
## MQTT Topics
### Incoming Commands
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/command`: Commands to control the system.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/config/update`: Update system configuration.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/ota/update`: Trigger OTA update.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/booking/paid`: Notify of paid booking.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/compartments/+/command`: Commands for specific compartments (e.g., open_gate, close_gate, query_state).
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/compartments/+/status`: Retained status updates for compartments.

### Outgoing Responses
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/response`: Responses to commands.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/compartments/+/ack`: Acknowledgments for compartment actions.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/debug`: Health telemetry every 60s (uptime, heap, fwVersion, battery, tasks, reconnects).
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/alert`: Alerts for errors, low power, etc.
- `waterfront/machine/{code}/status`: Machine status updates.
- `waterfront/slots/{id}/status`: Slot-specific status.
- `waterfront/locations/{code}/depositRelease`: Deposit release notifications.
- `waterfront/locations/{code}/returnConfirm`: Return confirmations.
- `waterfront/{location}/{code}/ota/status`: OTA update status.

## Testing
Run unit tests with `pio test`. Tests cover config loading, MQTT handling, sensor logic, and more. Coverage is at least 90%.

